# GemCities

Free Gemini capsule hosting. No server required.

Sign up, write gemtext, publish. That is the whole thing.

=> https://gemcities.com  Sign up or log in (web)

---

## What You Get

* A capsule at username.gemcities.com
* A web-based gemtext editor with live preview
* 50 MB of storage — generous for plain text
* One-click export of all your files at any time
* No ads, no tracking, no analytics. Ever.

The service is free and supported by donations.

---

## Getting Started

=> https://gemcities.com/register  Create an account
=> https://gemcities.com/editor    Open the editor

If you are new to Gemini, a capsule is what this protocol calls a site. Gemtext is the simple text format used to write them. The editor on the web side will show you a live preview as you write.

